        "subject": "LU-5050 libcfs: default CPT matches NUMA topology",
        "message": "LU-5050 libcfs: default CPT matches NUMA topology\n\nChange default value of CPT pattern and make it match NUMA topology.\n\nFix cfs_trimwhite() so that it doesn't try to modify the input string\nif it is already free of whitespace and has a trailing NUL.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=conf-sanity\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <andreas.dilger@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I3602cd0f391437b7d56e73d935b390f69a52a29a\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
